Contact Us
Our preferred method of communication is via email, please feel free to contact us.
**Please Note: CampusCare is your health benefits coverage program, we are NOT a clinic where you can obtain medical services. Please contact your CampusCare Primary Care Provider for all appointments, medical issues, or medical questions.**






